              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " used in electronics. One can implement a Schmitt-trigger-like action in the digital domain with a state machine:\nS1: when a 0->1 event occurs, go to state S2.\nS2: when a 1->0 event occurs go back to state S1.\n(I think of the timer variant as a Schmitt trigger that deals with analog signals)."
              }
